{"tid":2145662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［歷史撚］義和團係喺庚子年邊日開始打烊人攻大使館？","createTime":"2020-08-08T07:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T14:22:06.000Z","uid":88663,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a9dbc045344c4eb8e2ca619d584c3db28b011656","tid":2145662,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:06:41.000Z","msg":"忽然間想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbb58ec8ced8e61b1e8c25695f0e5f5442bd6f5","tid":2145662,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"有冇人知？"},{"pid":"85b32b0baf29feb721f5cefe224065111d480e01","tid":2145662,"uid":88663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsB01Ks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsB01Ks.png&h=d1c5100e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n極度義憤了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a92a82651678e6f543ed585068973a6f69c2a4a","tid":2145662,"uid":25260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b32b0baf29feb721f5cefe224065111d480e01","tid":2145662,"uid":88663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsB01Ks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsB01Ks.png&h=d1c5100e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n極度義憤了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:57:49.000Z","msg":"義憤就要填膺"},{"pid":"440ae8fbe16b2f52982a0398587ed9280ca9c1c6","tid":2145662,"uid":326712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"6月20日前，義和團對使館的唯一進攻性行動發生於6月14日。據竇納樂記載，這天夜間，義和團對使館哨兵「進行了好幾次攻擊」，但都被「輕易地擊退」[76]。顯然，這只是少數義和團的零星活動，並未構成對使館的真正威脅。6月20日之後，義和團對使館的圍攻也只是輔助性的，圍攻使館的主力一直是清軍[55]。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外國使館在北京東交民巷，受清兵圍困方位圖。<br />\n6月20日下午四點，清軍開始攻打使館，遂展開了55天的圍攻。6月20日至24日，攻勢比較猛烈。6月25日短暫停火，之後很快開始了更加猛烈的進攻。竇納樂報告說，6月25日夜半重新開始的射擊，是「迄今所遭受的最猛烈的炮火」[77]。6月25日至7月13日，幾乎每天都有激烈的戰鬥，使館防線一次次被突破，險情不斷出現。7月13日，清軍發動空前猛烈的全線進攻。7月14日，進攻減弱，更大的變化發生於7月16日，即天津陷落兩天之後。此後，對使館的進攻暫時停止[55]。"},{"pid":"2e73a67d03b477f2c7f1b95a5322eebea8300315","tid":2145662,"uid":326712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"8月1日起，清軍恢復對使館的炮擊，但猛烈程度遠不如7月13日以前。8月11日起，清軍重新對使館發動猛攻，直到北京陷落為止。8月4日，聯軍開始進軍北京。8月12日，占領通州。8月14日，聯軍攻入北京[55]。"},{"pid":"64aeef4fed131b28ad89e2bc389e96706ec07fd0","tid":2145662,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e73a67d03b477f2c7f1b95a5322eebea8300315","tid":2145662,"uid":326712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"8月1日起，清軍恢復對使館的炮擊，但猛烈程度遠不如7月13日以前。8月11日起，清軍重新對使館發動猛攻，直到北京陷落為止。8月4日，聯軍開始進軍北京。8月12日，占領通州。8月14日，聯軍攻入北京[55]。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:16:29.000Z","msg":"哦&hellip;&hellip;八月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a2b224ab2dfdb99c7ed16da8c11fa792a57528","tid":2145662,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e73a67d03b477f2c7f1b95a5322eebea8300315","tid":2145662,"uid":326712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"8月1日起，清軍恢復對使館的炮擊，但猛烈程度遠不如7月13日以前。8月11日起，清軍重新對使館發動猛攻，直到北京陷落為止。8月4日，聯軍開始進軍北京。8月12日，占領通州。8月14日，聯軍攻入北京[55]。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"哦&hellip;&hellip;八月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd904a0bdeb8b0ccb9234d35c3587ddcc574f7e","tid":2145662,"uid":213812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b32b0baf29feb721f5cefe224065111d480e01","tid":2145662,"uid":88663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsB01Ks.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsB01Ks.png&h=d1c5100e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n極度義憤了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"佢up乜撚嘢?攞緊大棒又會變咗石頭整親自己腳?打棒球?"},{"pid":"78e5647edeb281baa902db0a724db5abec7809d2","tid":2145662,"uid":36780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80a2b224ab2dfdb99c7ed16da8c11fa792a57528","tid":2145662,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e73a67d03b477f2c7f1b95a5322eebea8300315","tid":2145662,"uid":326712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"8月1日起，清軍恢復對使館的炮擊，但猛烈程度遠不如7月13日以前。8月11日起，清軍重新對使館發動猛攻，直到北京陷落為止。8月4日，聯軍開始進軍北京。8月12日，占領通州。8月14日，聯軍攻入北京[55]。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"哦&hellip;&hellip;八月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:25:38.000Z","msg":"我都好似明左小小野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b98e0e5c961688c2e6acb8a2c02205558186a04","tid":2145662,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"仲未有小粉紅圍美國大使館<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343ef5a7079f8dc881d75a6217621e66348a4ac5","tid":2145662,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b98e0e5c961688c2e6acb8a2c02205558186a04","tid":2145662,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"仲未有小粉紅圍美國大使館<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:41:56.000Z","msg":"聽黨話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟黨走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c53dd2f60c1438a5c221bdfbdc4ceced675796","tid":2145662,"uid":292416,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:56:37.000Z","msg":"明明係自己地頭但打成個幾月都搞唔掂個使館<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4beab76d78156bfde97e55c6dd41da92ec0da03e","tid":21